{
  "id": "6a00122d30eda69a3be19a4c",
  "title": "Gemini Protocol",
  "created": 1778389589,
  "updated": 1778390716,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a00122d30eda69a3be19a4c",
      "text": "Gemini Protocol",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778389589,
      "updated": 1778389589
    },
    {
      "id": "6a001255000000000008360e",
      "text": "[HTTP]及び[HTTPS]上のハイパーテキスト空間の代替",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778389589,
      "updated": 1778389680
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0012670000000000083610",
      "text": " である[Gopher Protocol]のモダンな代替として開発された",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778389607,
      "updated": 1778389639
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0016170000000000083635",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390551,
      "updated": 1778390551
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0016170000000000083636",
      "text": "[https://geminiprotocol.net/ Project Gemini]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390551,
      "updated": 1778390551
    },
    {
      "id": "6a001256000000000008360f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778389591,
      "updated": 1778389591
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0012b10000000000083612",
      "text": "[Fediverse]界隈とまあまあ親和性があるけど、よりマニアックにFreeでOpenを希求する人たちが使っている",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778389682,
      "updated": 1778389926
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00142c000000000008362a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390060,
      "updated": 1778390060
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0013d40000000000083622",
      "text": "仕様",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778389972,
      "updated": 1778389978
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0013c80000000000083621",
      "text": " (確か)CSSに相当するものがない",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778389961,
      "updated": 1778389978
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0014090000000000083627",
      "text": " \tCLIと親和性が高い",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390025,
      "updated": 1778390034
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0014120000000000083628",
      "text": " \t\t[ハイパーテキスト]はそもそもかくあるべきだ、という思想",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390035,
      "updated": 1778390402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0015850000000000083631",
      "text": " \t\t\t正直[CSS組版]なんかが出ている[World Wide Web]はデザイン性が無駄に高すぎ",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390405,
      "updated": 1778390438
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0013db0000000000083623",
      "text": " 動的な要素は初期のCGIレベルしか認められない",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778389979,
      "updated": 1778389999
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0013f10000000000083625",
      "text": " \t検索とBBSレベルの投稿しか見かけなかった",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390001,
      "updated": 1778390327
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0013fc0000000000083626",
      "text": " 色とフォントは全てクライアント側で設定される",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390013,
      "updated": 1778390254
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0014ef0000000000083630",
      "text": " \tCLIと親和性が高いことも関係している",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390255,
      "updated": 1778390263
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0015a60000000000083632",
      "text": " [- Markdownの劣化にしか見えない]独自の構文を採用",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390439,
      "updated": 1778390456
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0015c10000000000083634",
      "text": " \t正直この規格の一番の欠点だと思う",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390466,
      "updated": 1778390695
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0015b80000000000083633",
      "text": "\t \t(改造)[Markdown]でよくないか[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390456,
      "updated": 1778390491
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0013dc0000000000083624",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778389980,
      "updated": 1778389981
    },
    {
      "id": "6a001399000000000008361d",
      "text": "[https://wiki.archlinux.jp/index.php/Gemini Gemini - ArchWiki]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778389914,
      "updated": 1778389914
    },
    {
      "id": "6a001336000000000008361a",
      "text": "[https://messagepassing.github.io/008-justright/02-kzys/ ちょうどいいインターネット、Gemini / kzys - Message Passing]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778389814,
      "updated": 1778389953
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0013c1000000000008361f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778389953,
      "updated": 1778389953
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00142f000000000008362b",
      "text": "逸話",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390063,
      "updated": 1778390064
    },
    {
      "id": "6a001431000000000008362d",
      "text": " [Google]の従業員が[広告ブロックブロック]を念頭に、広範な[DRM]をWeb標準に求めることを検討した際にGNUな界隈でかなり話題になった（個人の感想です[hoagecko.icon]）",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390065,
      "updated": 1778390209
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0014b1000000000008362f",
      "text": " \t[https://github.com/explainers-by-googlers/Web-Environment-Integrity/blob/main/explainer.md Web-Environment-Integrity/explainer.md at main · explainers-by-googlers/Web-Environment-Integrity]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390193,
      "updated": 1778390194
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0016af0000000000083637",
      "text": " \t\t現在上記のプロジェクトは凍結済み",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778390704,
      "updated": 1778390716
    },
    {
      "id": "6a001430000000000008362c",
